    <item>
      <title>特朗普支持国际刑事法院对加沙地带实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-backs-international-criminal-court-sanctions-amid-gaza-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统批准对调查美国及其盟友的国际刑事法院官员实施制裁，重启其第一任期内的一项政策，针对该组织，他称其对美国主权构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-backs-international-criminal-court-sanctions-amid-gaza-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 21:29:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中情局新招募人员名单可能被对手利用数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/cia-list-of-new-recruits-risks-adversaries-exploiting-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统寻求削减联邦工作人员规模之际，美国中央情报局为遵守行政命令，将新招募的人员名单放在一封非机密电子邮件中发送给白宫，此举可能为额外的国家安全风险打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/cia-list-of-new-recruits-risks-adversaries-exploiting-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 21:07:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CFTC 代理主席 Pham 撤掉了正在调查她的人力资源主管</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/cftc-acting-chair-pham-removes-the-hr-head-investigating-her</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国商品期货交易委员会代理主席 Caroline Pham 撤掉了该机构的人力资源主管，后者正在领导一项内部调查，调查员工对 Pham 创造恶劣工作环境的投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/cftc-acting-chair-pham-removes-the-hr-head-investigating-her</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 20:47:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普收购案以 50,000 人的价格成交，焦点转向表现不佳的公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-buyout-at-50-000-takers-as-focus-shifts-to-poor-performers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，唐纳德·特朗普总统提出的联邦雇员辞职的提议已经被 50,000 多名工作人员接受。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-buyout-at-50-000-takers-as-focus-shifts-to-poor-performers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 20:08:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TSA 工作人员被告知他们不能接受马斯克的“买断”提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/tsa-workers-were-told-they-can-t-take-musk-s-fork-in-the-road</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国联邦工作人员收到延期辞职要约两天后，运输安全管理局向其数万名员工澄清说，他们不允许参与。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/tsa-workers-were-told-they-can-t-take-musk-s-fork-in-the-road</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 20:04:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>央行行长称通胀风险更加双面化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/inflation-risks-much-more-two-sided-top-central-banker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际清算银行总经理阿古斯丁·卡斯滕斯表示，消费价格风险已变得更加难以预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/inflation-risks-much-more-two-sided-top-central-banker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 19:56:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官暂时叫停特朗普和马斯克的联邦工作人员“买断”计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/judge-halts-trump-musk-federal-worker-buyout-until-feb-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着有关买断措施合法性的争论不断推进，一名法官暂时推迟了数百万联邦工作人员决定是否接受特朗普政府提出的辞职提议（并承诺数月全薪）的 2 月 6 日最后期限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/judge-halts-trump-musk-federal-worker-buyout-until-feb-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 18:24:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bessent 称马斯克的 DOGE 不会改变财政体系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bessent-says-musk-s-doge-isn-t-tinkering-with-treasury-systems</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特 (Scott Bessent) 表示，他亲自审查了伊隆·马斯克政府效率团队中对联邦支付数据具有只读权限的财政部员工，并且表示他们没有对该部门的支付系统进行“改动”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bessent-says-musk-s-doge-isn-t-tinkering-with-treasury-systems</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 18:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马领导人指责美国在运河争端中“撒谎”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/panama-leader-accuses-us-of-lies-in-dispute-over-canal-tolls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统何塞·劳尔·穆利诺否认他的政府已允许美国政府船只自由通过巴拿马运河，以回应唐纳德·特朗普收回水道的威胁，并指责美国“撒谎和虚假”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/panama-leader-accuses-us-of-lies-in-dispute-over-canal-tolls</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 17:22:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
